#Product Recommendation System

This project recommends products to users based on their preferences using Machine Learning techniques.

🔍 Project Steps

- Data collection and preprocessing
- Feature extraction
- Similarity calculation
- Generating recommendations

🤖 Model Used

- Content-Based Filtering

📊 Result

The system successfully recommends similar products based on user input.

📁 Dataset

Product dataset used for building recommendation system

🚀 Tools Used

- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Google Colab
